title: Joe Biden tells a different version of the bin Laden raid decision
text: Joe Biden tells a different version of the bin Laden raid decision Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (16 minutes ago) The vice president said he supported the raid, a departure from his previous descriptions of the debate that took place among the president and his cabinet members The vice president said Tuesday that he supported the decision to go after the al Qaeda leader - a departure from his previous statements CBS News 2 hours ago - Politics The vice president's claim appears to contradict his previous account of the president's decision. Politico 3 hours ago - Politics You Might Like
